0Switzerland%20to%20Dubai%20and%20its%20sleepier%2C%20smaller%20sister%20city%2C%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20is%20cementing%20the%20UAE's%20status%20as%20an%20international%20business%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20number%20of%20workers%20is%20still%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20who%20work%20at%20financial%20services%20firms%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-hedge-fund-investors-are-based-new-york-us-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-hedge-fund-investors-based-london-hong-kong-dubai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELondon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20DIFC's%20working%20population%20increased%209%25%20from%202024%2C%20and%20the%20area%20now%20boasts%2048%2C000%20people%20working%20in%20finance%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20peacock%20walks%20between%20outdoor%20tables%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffc339c007ca8c2737b4f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeacocks%20walking%20through%20outdoor%20sitting%20areas%20in%20the%20DIFC%20are%20common.%3Cp%3EBradley%20Saacks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20anecdotally%2C%20the%20seniority%20of%20the%20transplants%20is%20often%20higher.%20Executives%20and%20wealthy%20founders%20like%20billionaire%20Bridgewater%20founder%20Ray%20Dalio%20are%20moving%20to%20the%20region%2C%20which%20is%20developing%20scores%20of%20high-end%20apartments%20and%20beachfront%20villas%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20prices%20in%20Dubai%20are%20up%2070%25%20since%20the%20end%20of%202019%2C%20Bloomberg%20has%20reported%2C%20and%20stop-and-go%20traffic%20jams%20filled%20with%20luxury%20cars%20and%20BYDs%2C%20often%20helmed%20by%20personal%20drivers%20and%20Ubers%2C%20are%20common%20during%20rush%20hour%20around%20the%20DIFC.%20Even%20at%20sprawling%2C%20swanky%20hotels%2C%20where%20central%20air%20conditioning%20is%20blasting%20at%20all%20times%2C%20the%20dull%20buzz%20of%20power%20saws%20and%20rhythmic%20pounding%20of%20jackhammers%20from%20nearby%20construction%20sites%20can%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20was%20on%20the%20ground%20last%20week%20in%20the%20expat-filled%20city%20for%20a%20pair%20of%20investment%20conferences%20in%20the%20DIFC%20%E2%80%94%20SuperReturn%20Dubai%20at%20the%20Ritz-Carlton%20and%20AIM%20Summit%20at%20the%20Jumeirah%20Emirates%20Towers%20%E2%80%94%20to%20understand%20life%20in%20the%20Gulf%20and%20meet%20those%20who%20have%20made%20the%20move.%20Many%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20because%20they%20are%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220243d43a-fb7f-4e61-97b0-00be6310b4f9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20Switzerland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20Switzerland%20became%20the%2020th%20century's%20defining%20example%20of%20a%20capitalist%20dream%20%E2%80%94%20valuing%20money-making%20opportunities%20over%20political%20tiffs%20%E2%80%94%20the%20UAE%20has%20morphed%20into%20its%2021st-century%20iteration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20portfolio%20managers%20who%20met%20with%20Business%20Insider%20in%20Dubai%20say%20there%20is%20a%20distinct%20lack%20of%20distractions%20to%20trading%20compared%20to%20their%20lives%20working%20in%20London%20or%20Hong%20Kong.%20Personal%20drivers%20and%20nannies%20are%20common%2C%20they%20say%2C%20and%20many%20also%20hire%20personal%20chefs%20who%20shop%20for%20them.%20While%20traffic%20is%20a%20constant%20annoyance%2C%20strikes%20and%20protests%20shutting%20down%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20relatively%20frequent%20in%20London%20and%20Paris%20%E2%80%94%20are%20nonexistent%20because%20it's%20not%20permitted%20by%20the%20Royal%20family%2C%20who%20control%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20immigration%20bec