0their%20long-term%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20portfolio%20managers%20and%20fundraisers%20said%20they%20didn't%20move%20with%20intentions%20of%20staying%20forever%2C%20but%20their%20families%20have%20come%20to%20enjoy%20the%20lifestyle.%20Summers%20%E2%80%94%20when%20temperatures%20reach%20levels%20that%20can%20melt%20car%20tires%2C%20as%20one%20individual%20claimed%20%E2%80%94%20are%20often%20spent%20in%20Europe%2C%20much%20like%20New%20Yorkers%20escaping%20to%20the%20Hamptons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWealthy%20people%20who%20once%20worried%20about%20their%20and%20their%20families'%20safety%20in%20cities%20like%20London%20now%20leave%20their%20wallets%20on%20tables%20in%20cafes%20to%20reserve%20their%20seats%20while%20they%20pick%20up%20their%20coffees.%20At%20the%20two%20conferences%2C%20laptops%20were%20left%20on%20tables%20and%20chairs%20in%20conference%20halls%20while%20attendees%20networked%20in%20the%20next%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20private%20banker%20who%20lived%20in%20London%20and%20Geneva%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20more%20chaos%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20better%20Dubai%20looks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20stability%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20also%20made%20the%20region%20attractive%20to%20invest%20in%20because%20of%20the%20confidence%20that%20long-term%20infrastructure%20projects%20will%20remain%20a%20government%20priority%2C%20several%20execs%20said%20%E2%80%94%20is%20tied%20directly%20to%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20whose%20portrait%20is%20omnipresent%20in%20Dubai%2C%20hanging%20in%20hotel%20lobbies%20and%20plastered%20on%20billboards%20on%20the%20main%20highway%20through%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Six%20portraits%20hang%20over%20the%20desk%20of%20a%20hotel%20receptionist%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffc3c2c007ca8c2737b516%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22