alance%20is%20restored.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-wikipedia-zero-investing-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecriticized%20his%20own%20Wikipedia%3C%2Fa%3E%20page%20on%20X%2C%20which%20was%20then%20Twitter%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bwar%20zone%20with%20a%20zillion%20edits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20looked%20at%20my%20wiki%20for%201st%20time%20in%20years.%20It's%20insane!%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20in%20a%20December%202019%20post.%20%26quot%3BBtw%2C%20can%20someone%20please%20delete%20'investor'.%20I%20do%20basically%20zero%20investing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20he%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20Wikipedia%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-trivial%20left-wing%20bias.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Wikipedia's%20cofounder%2C%20Jimmy%20Wales%2C%20also%20have%20a%20long-running%20online%20feud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwikipedia-jimmy-wales-elon-musk-criticism-censoring-tweets-turkey-election-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWales%20criticized%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20restricting%20some%20content%20on%20Twitter%20in%20Turkey%20before%20the%20country's%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20November%202023%2C%20after%20Musk%20rebranded%20Twitter%20to%20X%2C%20Wales%20said%20X%20was%20overrun%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwikipedia-jimmy-wales-x-twitter-trolls-elon-musk-fight-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Btrolls%20and%20lunatics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Wales'%20comment%20saying%20Wikipedia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-warned-wikipedia-is-not-for-sale-by-founder-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewas%20not%20for%20sale%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Musk%20wrote%20in%20October%202023%20that%20he%20would%20give%20the%20pl