een%20supported%20by%20geopolitical%20uncertainty%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration%20and%20concerns%20over%20US%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20gold%20prices%20started%20heading%20sharply%20lower%20after%20hitting%20their%20record%20high%2C%20a%20move%20that%20many%20have%20been%20expecting%20due%20to%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-record-price-today-4000-stock-market-rally-hedge-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erapid%20runup%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price-today-forecast-outlook-wall-street-boom-goldman-sachs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20cited%20speculative%20unwinds%20and%20spillover%20from%20the%20silver%20market%20for%20the%20slump.%20Still%2C%20the%20bank%20expects%20central%20banks%20and%20institutional%20investors%20to%20boost%20gold%20exposure%20amid%20global%20uncertainty.%20It%20has%20a%20gold%20price%20forecast%20of%20%244%2C900%20per%20ounce%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20bulls%20include%20Ed%20Yardeni%2C%20a%20market%20veteran%2C%20who%20has%20a%20%2410%2C000%20an%20ounce%20call%20for%20gold%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20is%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapital%20Economics%20predicts%20that%20the%20price%20of%20gold%20will%20fall%20to%20%243%2C500%20an%20ounce%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026%20as%20the%20precious%20metal%20heads%20toward%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini-bust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20firm%20also%20doesn't%20expect%20central%20banks%20to%20keep%20adding%20to%20their%20gold%20holdings%20as%20the%20share%20of%20the%20yellow%20metal%20in%20total%20reserves%20has%20surpassed%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-outlook-forec