black%20jacket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69002e2c0be9845f2dc533be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221774%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJonathan%20Ross%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20AI%20chip%20company%20Groq%2C%20said%20an%20AI%20bubble%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsign%20that%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20economic%20activity%20going%20on%20and%20you%20just%20attract%20all%20sorts%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJonathan%20Ross%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20AI%20chip%20startup%2C%20Groq.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERoss%20said%20people%20should%20want%20an%20AI%20bubble%20because%20it%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20economic%20activity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvesting%20in%20the%20AI%20boom%20will%20largely%20pay%20off%20if%20people%20bet%20on%20%26quot%3Breal%20AI%20innovations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20chip%20startup%20Groq's%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjonathan-ross-groq-ai-power-list-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20having%20an%20AI%20bubble%20may%20not%20be%20a%20bad%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20was%20speaking%20to%20CNBC's%20Dan%20Murphy%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Future%20Investment%20Initiative%20summit%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20AI%20was%20experiencing%20a%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20subtlety%20and%20nuance%20here.%20So%20the%20thing%20is%2C%20as%20always%2C%20you%20do%20want%20a%20bubble%20because%20the%20bubble%20is%20the%20sign%20that%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20economic%20activity%20going%20on%2C%20and%20you%20just%20attract%20all%20sorts%20of%20people%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20told%20Murphy%20that%20the%20real%20question%20isn't%20whether%20there%20is%20an%20AI%20bubble%2C%20but%20whether%20people%20are%20making%20the%20ri