engers%20must%20be%20accommodated%2C%20the%20cost%20can%20increase%20to%20%24200%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268af1876-df9d-45a1-ad9b-f8d357d27ec8%5C%22%3EBeing%20outside%20a%20base%20made%20things%20trickier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20tracking%20website%20FlightRadar24%20shows%20the%20original%20aircraft%20took%20off%20four%20hours%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-pilot-thirty-years-career-salary-pay-captain-airlines-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFormer%20Delta%20pilot%20Mark%20Stephens%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20mechanic%20and%20replacement%20slide%20may%20have%20been%20flown%20in%20to%20address%20the%20problem%20if%20there%20wasn't%20a%20fix%20on-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20swapping%20the%20A220%20in%20Pittsburgh%20%E2%80%94%20where%20Delta%20doesn't%20have%20a%20major%20hub%20%E2%80%94%20is%20logistically%20trickier%20than%20at%20a%20hub%20like%20Atlanta%20or%20Detroit%2C%20where%20spare%20planes%20are%20more%20readily%20available%20to%20get%20passengers%20on%20their%20way%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERebooking%20may%20also%20be%20easier%20in%20a%20base%20with%20more%20route%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20said%20passengers%20on%20the%20return%20flight%20were%20rebooked%20on%20later%20departures%2C%20with%20hotel%20rooms%20provided%20to%20those%20who%20had%20to%20stay%20overnight.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20slide%20deployment%20mistake%20is%20not%20unheard%20of.%20Airbus%20said%20that%20roughly%2030%20to%2040%20inadvertent%20deployments%20happen%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20a%20British%20Airways%20crew%20member%20accidentally%20set%20off%20a%20slide%20on%20an%20Airbus%20A321%20%E2%80%94%20an%20error%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fnews%2F32785128%2Fbritish-airways-crew-activates-plane-slide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20could%20cost%20about%20%24130%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20sometimes%20passengers%20set%20them%20off.%20In%20October%2C%20a%20United%20Airlines%20passenger%20tried%20to%20open%20a%20door%20after%20landing%20in%20Houston.%20The%20Boeing%20737%20door%20didn't%20open%2C%20but%20it%20still%20triggered%20the%20evacuation%20slide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-crew-members-slide-mistake-may-cost-the-airline-thousands-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761596931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ffcfce599d46a4ccc0eed4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-crew-members-slide-mistake-may-cost-the-airline-thousands-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Repackaging%20alone%20could%20cost%20Delta%20around%20%2412%2C000.%20Factoring%20in%20passenger%20accommodations%20and%20any%20slide%20repair%20could%20push%20the%20bill%20to%20six%20figures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22trains%40insider.com%20(Taylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-crew-members-slide-mistake-may-cost-the-airline-thousands-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wayfair%20Way%20Day%20Sale%3A%20Save%20up%20to%2080%25%20on%20our%20favorite%20furniture%20and%20home%20decor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Split%20image%20featuring%20Wayfair%20home%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20left%2C%20a%20cozy%20bedroom%20with%20floral%20wallpaper%2C%20an%20orange%20bed%20frame%2C%20and%20a%2